description.en: fnbr.co was created to serve as a directory for Fortnite Cosmetics and help spread community awareness of items within Fortnite Battle Royale.
description.ga_IE: Cruthaíodh FNBR.CO chun fónamh mar eolaire le haghaidh cosmaidí Fortnite agus cabhraigh le feasacht an phobail a scaipeadh ar mhíreanna laistigh de Chath na Fortite Royale.
